<Layout title="Projects - Saki Portfolio">
  <h1>Projects</h1>
  <p>Here are some of the key hardware and firmware projects I've worked on recently:</p>

  <section>
    <h2>PDM Microphone to PCM Audio on Nordic nRF</h2>
    <p>
      Captured high-fidelity digital microphone data using the Nordic nRF52 PDM (Pulse Density Modulation) peripheral and converted/filtered it into ready-to-use PCM audio buffers via DMA-based transfer mechanisms.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Platform:</strong> Nordic nRF52 series</li>
      <li><strong>Topics:</strong> PDM, PCM, DMA, double buffering, audio decimation</li>
      <li><strong>Language:</strong> C</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>STM32 SDMMC + DMA Debugging</h2>
    <p>
      Diagnosed and resolved critical race conditions, interrupt preemption priorities, and memory coherence issues on STM32 microcontroller DMA transfers to SD cards via SDMMC protocol.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Platform:</strong> STM32L4 series</li>
      <li><strong>Topics:</strong> SDMMC, DMA, NVIC, RTOS Preemption, Cache Coherence</li>
      <li><strong>Language:</strong> C</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>